<i>Wabi-Sabi Subs presents:</i>
<b>SHINYA SHOKUDO Season 3</b>
EP 6: "Cabbage Rolls..."

22
00:02:06,811 --> 00:02:13,053
<i>When the autumn chill comes, there are many
customers who'd order cabbage rolls.</i>

23
00:02:13,327 --> 00:02:17,000
<i>I prepare lots of pieces beforehand.</i>

24
00:02:17,116 --> 00:02:20,230
<i>After all, it's quite a
time-consuming process.</i>

25
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:25,590
How long has it been now?

26
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,560
Almost three months by now.

27
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,160
Surprisingly long, huh?

28
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:36,900
But the guy this time is unusual...
considering that Marilyn's types are good-looking guys.

29
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:45,830
The man I look for is not his face...
but his mind and fingers.

30
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:52,920
<i>His name is Kimitoshi-kun but...
he's working in a nearby osteopathic clinic...</i>

31
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:57,880
<i>Marilyn seemed to have met him there
