to contact her mother for the first time in 10 years.

70
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,480
Welcome

71
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:37,380
Mari-chan, you came back so soon.

72
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,240
Master, shochu with hot water.

73
