We were worried about you. Just now we
were asking Kimi-kun about you.

76
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,160
Is that so.

77
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:54,560
So how's your mom?

78
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:58,370
Turns out there was nothing wrong with her.

79
00:05:59,452 --> 00:06:01,150
Regardless of it,
his hands seem pretty fast.

80
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:05,040
No matter how busy, he'll do it.

81
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,830
Mariko?

82
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:17,950
You came all the way home, huh.

83
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:21,720
You called me up and said,
"Come home quick", didn't you?

84
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,840
This is my daughter, Mariko.

85
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:28,830
