On second thought, I guess this is
too much for me to take.

153
00:12:01,859 --> 00:12:04,419
Please stop!

154
00:12:06,529 --> 00:12:09,859
Mari-chan, please don't
do this anymore!

155
00:12:17,099 --> 00:12:19,069
<i>Is it supposed to be like that?</i>

156
00:12:33,469 --> 00:12:35,879
Don't embarrass me.

157
00:12:37,469 --> 00:12:40,549
I guess I wasn't able to stand it.

158
00:12:41,549 --> 00:12:45,289
Even if it's strip teasing...
it is my vocation.

159
00:12:45,789 --> 00:12:47,429
Don't ever stop my performance.

160
00:12:48,589 --> 00:12:51,529
But I am also a man so...

161
00:12:52,509 --> 00:12:56,069
If you're a man, you should
accept everything about me.

162
00:12:58,629 --> 00:13:01,139
Excuse me.

163
00:13:02,549 --> 00:13:07,069
Oh, it's the boyfriend!
That was a cool thing you did awhile ago.

164
00:13:07,069 --> 00:13:09,219
I thought you should have
done that from the start.

165
00:13:14,269 --> 00:13:16,399
Sorry to disturb.

166
00:13:23,709 --> 00:13:26,769
Did you have fun seeing your daughter naked?

167
00:13:26,829 --> 00:13:28,439
Did you see me?

168
00:13:32,629 --> 00:13:35,979
You might not know it but I can see
the audience very clearly.

169
00:13:36,309 --> 00:13:38,809
It's not just the face that a child
inherits from her parents...

170
00:13:38,869 --> 00:13:43,079
Your boobs were exactly like mine
when I was younger.

171
00:13:44,459 --> 00:13:49,559
But how long are you gonna
do this kind of work?

172
00:13:50,629 --> 00:13:56,629
I swear... you've never recognized anything
that I've done.

173
00:13:56,989 --> 00:14:00,629
Even in the hospital, what was that?
"My daughter, the dancer."

174
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:03,469
It's fine to call me a "stripper".

175
00:14:03,509 --> 00:14:05,939
I will dance even if I become an old woman.

176
00:14:06,159 --> 00:14:09,059
You're still so obstinate.

177
00:14:09,059 --> 00:14:11,509
You haven't changed at all
since you were a kid.

178
00:14:11,719 --> 00:14:14,159
Go home already.

179
00:14:14,459 --> 00:14:17,549
My next performance is gonna start.

180
00:14:29,429 --> 00:14:30,669
It was good.

181
00:14:32,219 --> 00:14:35,239
<i>After a few days...</i>

182
00:14:36,109 --> 00:14:39,389
- I see. You'll be taking the bus home tomorrow.
- Yeah.

183
00:14:39,389 --> 00:14:41,769
But is it really okay, with Marilyn and all...

184
00:14:41,989 --> 00:14:47,359
It's fine. After all, we'll just gonna
start arguing again anyway so...

185
00:14:47,509 --> 00:14:50,389
Anyway, for now, I've told her already
that I'm getting married.

186
00:14:50,389 --> 00:14:51,549
What?

187
00:14:52,069 --> 00:14:53,669
You're getting married?

188
00:14:54,309 --> 00:14:58,259
You see, my current boyfriend
had proposed to me.

189
00:14:59,149 --> 00:15:03,359
I've dated a lot of men but...
I wonder if this one's the last.

190
00:15:03,629 --> 00:15:05,999
Is that so. I see...

191
00:15:06,389 --> 00:15:07,839
What kind of person is he?

192
00:15:08,269 --> 00:15:12,669
He's the plainest guy
I ever dated, but still...

193
00:15:12,669 --> 00:15:16,109
Yuu-chan somehow, isn't like the other guys.

194
00:15:16,229 --> 00:15:18,649
So he's different.

195
00:15:19,309 --> 00:15:25,059
Yuu-chan has a weird taste,
he wants to marry a sick person.

196
00:15:25,469 --> 00:15:26,899
Sick person!?

197
00:15:28,069 --> 00:15:32,029
Actually, I came to Tokyo
for a health check-up.

198
00:15:32,149 --> 00:15:33,129
Check-up?

199
00:15:33,989 --> 00:15:35,129
